    <release version="46.3" date="2024-06-10">
      <description>
        <p>This release includes important bugfixes and translation updates.</p>
        <p>Ptyxis will now default the standard input (stdin) of shells to blocking status as is generally expected from user shells.</p>
        <p>When requesting Ptyxis run a custom command using "--" or "--execute" no longer will warning banners be displayed for quickly exiting processes as long as the process exits nominally.</p>
      </description>
    </release>
